snippet.title: BADLAND: Game of the Year Edition Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/269670/
With BADLAND: Game of the Year Edition, experience the multi-award-winning action adventure like never before - redesigned for Steam with new controls, local multiplayer awesomeness, lots of content & enhanced above full-HD visuals.
